<plot>In the 60's, the admiral Sampaio Barroso returns to his farm for the wedding of his daughter Bebel. She will get married with her cousin Toni, in a marriage arranged to save the wealthy of the family. On the wedding, they meet with their cousin Ticão, who lives in the farm and loves Bebel. Ticão tries to sabotage the ceremony to avoid the wedding of Bebel and Toni.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?081771</url></doc>
